15,01                              Harvest Moon
15,01                              ~~~~~~~~~~~~

15,01Silent years slipping by,
15,01Oblivious to the sweeping hands of time,
15,01Still the miser Fates watch o'er,
15,01And sleepless Destiny wields its sword.

15,01Thy field is white, the grain hast grown,
15,01Unyielding Time hast overshone,
15,01The sickle thrust into the field,
15,01The sweeping arm which shall not yield.

15,01While through the chaff the reaper sifts,
15,01Weighed in scales and found bereft,
15,01The Harvest Moon like times before,
15,01Pale and coolly shadows o'er.

15,01                                  .Ts.
